Speaker 1: Fort Chester, New York.

Speaker 2: And then as far as the first order that you placed, how are you doing on those?

Speaker 1: Yeah, I still have a few left.

Speaker 1: And then I'll send it to you.

Speaker 2: they gave me this whole thing, and they did a list of things, and they were saying, like,

Speaker 1: these things definitely stay away from.

Speaker 2: Now, whether that's really true or not, who knows?

Speaker 1: It could all be just a sales gimmick.

Speaker 2: So I went with that, and that's why I went with those.

Speaker 1: But, you know, before I did that, I did contact my doctor.

Speaker 1: Now I'm starting to, you know, date again, and I'm going to be sexually active.

Speaker 2: And I was like, for the first time in my life, I'm kind of a one and done kind of thing.

Speaker 2: But, you know, at 67, it doesn't work that way.

Speaker 1: And, you know, it was my first time realizing that.

Speaker 2: You know, I never had that issue.

Speaker 1: So, I mean, that's why I did it.

Speaker 2: But he just said a low dose, so that's why I got those.

Speaker 1: But if it's really not doing anything for me, then what's the point in spending the money, you know?

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: So, like I said before, I really don't want to sell you anything.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: If we do have something that can work and give you that kick that you're absolutely looking for, Dominic,

Speaker 2: I want to see if I have the different variation available to send you as a sample for free.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: I'll message the pharmacy and have them send you over 10 free pills of the AGV that's made in our France factory.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: With Pfizer.

Speaker 1: So, it'll be a little bit more potent on the dosage.

Speaker 2: It'll stay at 50, but it'll give you the—I guarantee this one's going to give you the kick that you're looking for.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: So, I'm going to send you 10 free pills.

Speaker 1: Try them out.

Speaker 2: I'll make sure everything in the future is paused for the time being for the next five months.

Speaker 1: I'll give you five months to try them.

Speaker 2: Call us back and let us know what the best refill schedule should be.

Speaker 1: All right.

Speaker 2: Thank you.

Speaker 1: All right.

Speaker 2: Sounds good.

Speaker 1: But I won't get any more of the other ones.

Speaker 2: I won't get another order of the other ones.

Speaker 1: Negative.

Speaker 2: No, the pill that you're going to be looking for now will have the number 50 pressed onto it like a stamp.

Speaker 1: Okay?

Speaker 2: All right.

Speaker 1: Thank you.

Speaker 2: Absolutely.

Speaker 1: Have a great one.

Speaker 2: You too.

Speaker 1: Bye.
